  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.244685440216932         -6.6582          -153.54          -642.42
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.066304410821452          1.8042            41.61           174.08
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.037756220620638         -1.0274           -23.69           -99.13
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.207207810891234          5.6384           130.02           544.02
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

